Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: In addition, this evening, we have to send our prayers and support to all the families affected by Hurricane Helene. This has been the worst Hurricane Response by a president and vice president since Katrina—and this is simply unacceptable... Kamala wined and dined in San Francisco, and all the people in North Carolina—no helicopters, no rescue. They’re offering $750 to people whose homes have been washed away—meanwhile, they send our money to other countries by the billions.
